1. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
2. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
3. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Food          | lettuce    | apple     |
| Color   | turquise       | fuchsia |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | bird      |
| Transport     | van        | quad-bike |

