.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-16::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite
There 2 different types of food: lemon, strawberry
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, march
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage    | sprite     | 7up           |
| Food        | lemon      | strawberry    |
| Birthday       | july    | march |
| Transport   | helicopter | bike          |

